The fit is often oversized - designed to be worn loosely, allowing the garment's design features to do all the work. The top is made up of angular panels which finish at different lengths, creating a choppy, up and down hemline. Layer over a contrasting coloured pants, dresses or skirts to show off the hemline to best effect.
